.TH LOA-READING-SMART-PREVIEW 1 "2026-03-15" "Library Of Alexandria" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
reading smart preview \- Preview recommended books based on interests
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> reading smart preview
.br
alexandria> reading smart preview 10
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Shows top recommendation candidates without changing the reading list.
.TP
Recommendations are based on your configured interests profile.
.TP
Optional count controls how many recommendations to show (default: 10).
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
alexandria> reading smart preview
.TP
alexandria> reading smart preview 6
